<div class="help-content-wrap"><h3 id="how-to-play-sports">How to Play &quot;Sports&quot;</h3>
<ol>
<li><p>Click on the &quot;Sports&quot; tab to check our &quot;popular&quot; events area.</p>
</li>
<li><p>View important prematch games in the &quot;Highlights&quot; area.</p>
</li>
<li><p>Browse ongoing live betting games or virtuals to place a bet.</p>
</li>
<li><p>We do not only provide sports betting for Football, but we also provide all kinds of bets for other sports.</p>
</li>
<li><p>Choose events you wish to play and select the odds by clicking on them. The chosen selections (no more than 30) will be automatically added to the betslip.</p>
</li>
<li><p>The amount of a Total Stake must always be between NGN 100-2,000,000. The value of every single stake should be no less than NGN 100. Click on &quot;Place Bet&quot; and &quot;Confirm&quot; the bet to place it.</p>
</li>
<li><p>A message will be displayed to inform whether a bet has been successfully placed or not.</p>
</li>
</ol>
</div>